The paper discusses a polystore system that supports diverse database systems working with different data models, which is a core concept in database systems (cs.DB). The system also deals with complex problems that span across different processing or storage engines, which is related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the application of the system on medical data, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or software engineering (cs.SE) if the focus is on the development of the system.
